sections.heading: relief; obtaining by fraud; penalty
sections.text: Any person who shall knowingly, by fraudulent representations, obtain or attempt to obtain any payment or aid herein provided for shall be guilty of a Class II misdemeanor.SourceLaws 1921, c. 40, ยง 5, p. 183;C.S.1922, ยง 6210;C.S.1929, ยง 80-405;R.S.1943, ยง 80-405;L
